Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:05.36,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}温柔地洒落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:09.44,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}大大的窗户中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:15.49,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}与你邂逅的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:19.79,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}感觉有些遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:27.38,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}一点一滴累积起来的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.26,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}温暖着我
