Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:38.93,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}紧密相连的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:44.30,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\be5\fad(600,500)}轻轻地向我诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:50.61,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}再次迎来这个季节时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:57.28,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}甚至连寻找你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:02.62,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}都无法办到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:07.94,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}我会永远都不忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:13.88,ED-CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(600,500)}直至与你再次相逢之日
